snippet.title: GMOGMediaTV
snippet.description:
Great Man of God Media LLC is a platform that provides suggestions on replacing the System of Racism (White Supremacy) that affects people of color (African descent) with a System of Justice. 

The channel covers 9 area's of activity:
1. Economics 
2. Education
3. Entertainment
4. Labor
5. Law
6. Politics
7. Religion
8. Sex
9. War/Counter-War

The popular segments include GMOGMedia Spotlight (Counter-Racism) VLOG's and more....
